{
  "stem": "422.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And you've got a document.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We're Polish girls.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They can't kill Polish girls, they won't kill.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Unless we're Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I said, we're going to mix together with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And whatever work they give me, I'm going to accept, to live through the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We followed them, and we stood on line, and we told them the same story, that we were working in this and that town.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the Russians are there already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we didn't want to be with the Russians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We're looking for work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We got work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I got a job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I was paid 120 marks a week.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "In Waldenburg, there was a big house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They call it-- it's like a hotel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "It was like a hotel for people-- for-- the high ranking people were there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I didn't know they sent me to a dangerous place again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But I had to accept.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "To be a chambermaid in a hotel, and the other one too, my friend.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "To make the beds, to clean, to help out a little bit in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they gave me a letter from the unemployment office to show that they need people to work in this place.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We went there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And the woman in charge of that-- of that hotel was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "That was-- she was from Polish mix, Polish and German parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And she heard me-- that I'm a Polish girl, she was very happy with me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "She said, I didn't have a chance to speak Polish in so many years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Now I'm going to refresh.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "She will refresh her Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "She hired me right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "She liked me, that woman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "But it was a dangerous place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "It was a lot of SS men there.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
